   HONG KONG
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Hong Kong yesterday succumbed to the recent rises in US interest rates and
announced a 0.25 percentage point increase in bank base rates to 6.75 per
cent, writes Simon Holberton in Hong Kong. The decision by Hongkong Bank and
